### Teste de Contrato - /api/games/shoot
### Caso 1: 401 sem token
POST https://goldeouro-backend-v2.fly.dev/api/games/shoot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10,
  "direction": "left"
}

### Caso 2: 403 token inválido
POST https://goldeouro-backend-v2.fly.dev/api/games/shoot
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token-invalido

{
  "amount": 10,
  "direction": "left"
}

### Caso 3: 200 com token válido
POST https://goldeouro-backend-v2.fly.dev/api/games/shoot
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 10,
  "direction": "left"
}

